Description: Hardly used great condition. No scratches, dings, or dents. May show signs of light use. Awesome tone and action. This is a prototype model and has "PROTO" stamped in the back of the headstock. It differs from the final production model by having neck through construction instead of a bolt on neck. Comes with decent gig bag.
